OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly dry day
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells. A few showers
OL,7,Fpossible but these mainly confined to
OL,8,Fthe north over Caithness and
OL,9,FSutherland. Light winds, but a little
OL,10,Fbreezier near showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening in the north
OL,13,Fwith a few showers, dry with clear
OL,14,Fspells elsewhere. Becoming cloudier
OL,15,Ffor all overnight with outbreaks of
OL,16,Frain in the north. Light northwesterly
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
