OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain in the morning spreading
OL,7,Fsouthwards through the day to reach
OL,8,FSkye and Lochaber later in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Drier in the north later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FHigh
OL,12,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,13,Fsettled few days with light winds.
OL,14,FCloudy at times, especially in the
OL,15,Fnorth and east but still plenty of
OL,16,Fbright and sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
